# codeyam-editor:start
# Managed by `codeyam-editor init` / `codeyam-editor start`.
# Do not edit between these markers — your changes will be overwritten.
# NOT ignored, deliberately: .codeyam/state/finalize-debt.json.
# `verify-full-finalize` compares the COMMITTED marker against the working
# tree, so ignoring it makes the gate impossible to ever pass. It is a
# committed artifact — like a lockfile. Do not add it here.
.codeyam/secrets.json
.codeyam/setup-connections.json
